title: The two knives
author: johnmedic
pages:
#- People say its two sides of the story,more like two knives.§0
§0This is a story of a nation§0
§0Once upon there was a nation callled Little Richard §0Island.Our§0 protagonist was a traveler who just arrived entered in the nation he was greeted  by the 
#- Leader of this §0nation.The§0 leader was very friendly,kind and really proud for his §0nation.The§0 traveler started his business,a bank to make his own §0currency.This§0 way he got even more close to the leader of this nation talking about the political system of 
#- the §0nation.He§0 met some more people two people who were even more close to the leader and someone who was accused to be a spy many §0time.The§0 traveler didnt believe them and he became friend with this §0person.Everything§0 was fine until one day the nation was 
#- attacked.The§0 leader was traveling while this happend and he told his people to wait for him but then the two people who where close to him started to fight for the §0leadership.One§0 of them became the leader and the other the "betrayer".The leader returned 
#- to his §0nation.He§0 tried to find his people but he couldnt find anyone then he managed to talk with the new §0leader.The§0 new leader accused the leader to be a §0tyrant.The§0 leader tried to talk with other people too but everyone was saying the same thing.
#- The traveler explained the leader that he cant just leave from those people and leader said "Stay if you want you could be a useful diplomat there" and the traveler said "Please dont hurt them" then the leader repleid "Dont worry I wont"
#- The next day traveler had to go to a very far away land to do some §0research.After§0 some days he got a §0mail.It§0 was from the person who was accused to be a spy."The Tyrant is trying to attacks us".When the traveler returned he found a ghost town.
#- He heard the leader has been put in prison.§0
§0
§0Nothing is right§0
§0Nothing is wrong§0
§0Only two knives to stab each other
